plan your next actions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965810/extras/14528972a675e0c5ae66f53c1c388722.poster.avif?t=1773809259\" aria-label=\"Piece The Clues Together\" width=780 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965810/extras/14528972a675e0c5ae66f53c1c388722.webm?t=1773809259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965810/extras/14528972a675e0c5ae66f53c1c388722.mp4?t=1773809259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At key points, you'll need to use the information in your notebook to piece together what evidence you have and deduce the facts. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965810/extras/5ab56339cdce8432083fac30129c6126.avif?t=1773809259\" alt=\"A Diverse Cast of Complex Characters\" width=780 height=404 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This story contains over 30 different characters with complex relationships leading to an intricate human drama between the cast. It's impossible to learn every little secret in one playthrough.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965810/extras/98e6d5b5c6bf4c11f404108930c940c5.avif?t=1773809259\" alt=\"Killer's Eye View\" width=780 height=286 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness snippets from the perspective of the murderer or their victim. Pay attention for subtle hints on where and what to investigate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965810/extras/759d56604e7b